nt":1},{"word":"feeble","count":1},{"word":"unfit","count":1},{"word":"sate","count":1},{"word":"hunger","count":1},{"word":"hero","count":1},{"word":"reign","count":1},{"word":"throne","count":1},{"word":"glory","count":1},{"word":"claimed","count":1},{"word":"weak","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"It... awaits you...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"A wise choice, Augusta...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"It is time. Return to where you belong. Fabianum has long awaited your homecoming...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Augusta...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"...Now you've seen it. {Male=His;Female=Her} tiny little Echo. Silencing the Dark Tide with such ease... Resonance power. Such might. Such perfection.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Confined to this frail human form, you will achieve nothing.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"You nearly lost everything... As you once did.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Augusta... do not resist the \"Gift of Divinity.\" Follow our guidance. Return to <te href=750016>Murmurstown</te>...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"To your home...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Brazen faithless one!","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Receive the judgment of the heavens","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"The sacred crucible shall reshape your soul","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Faithless one... The strength you refused shall now become the blade that strikes you down...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"To spurn a divine gift is to invite consequence, and Divinity offers mercy but once...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"The Dark Tide answers only to strength. Those without it are doomed to be forsaken...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Augusta, my brave yet fragile child… Your strength is far too feeble, unfit to sate the hunger of the Dark Tide.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"You long to become a hero, to reign by might… But tell me... can the throne of glory be claimed by one so weak?","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002}]}